					"value": "With companion Karlach kill Gortash and go through her dialog with Gortash corpse. Then when she leaves speak with her again at the camp. \r\nFor camp behaviour recruit Karlach and send to camp, then kill Gortash, speak back to her and select \"$Karlach, about Gortash. I killed him.\""
